citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:15 am on 05-
JAN-23.
The inspector arrived at the facility at 11:15 am and spoke to member of the household who stated no adult was available.
The inspector then called the licensee and left a message and sent a text message. The licensee communicated with the
inspector through text message to confirm no adult was available for the inspection.
End Section

Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:15 am on 05-

The inspector arrived at the facility at 11:15 am and spoke to member of the household who stated no adult was available.  
The inspector then called the licensee and left a message and sent a text message.  The licensee communicated with the 
inspector through text message to confirm no adult was available for the inspection. 
 
 
 
End Section
